or%20Brutal%20Murder%20Of%20Plastic%20Surgeon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20son%20of%20a%20well-known%20Spanish%20actor%20has%20been%20sentenced%20to%20life%20imprisonment%20for%20killing%20and%20dismembering%20a%20man%20on%20the%20Thai%20island%20of%20Koh%20Phangan%20last%20year.%20Daniel%20Sancho%20Bronchalo%2C%20the%20son%20of%20television%20star%20Rodolfo%20Sancho%20Aguirre%2C%20claimed%20he%20acted%20in%20self-defence%20when%20he%20killed%20Colombian%20plastic%20surgeon%20Edwin%20Arrieta%20Arteaga.%20He%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20the%20murder%20in%20August%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2C%20noindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcwyxry3k9rgo%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESancho%2C%20now%2030%2C%20told%20the%20Spanish%20news%20agency%20EFE%20at%20the%20time%20that%20he%20had%20been%20a%20%26quot%3Bhostage%26quot%3B%20to%20Arrieta%2C%20whom%20he%20described%20as%20obsessed%20with%20him.%20The%20case%20has%20attracted%20significant%20attention%20in%20Spain%2C%20with%20many%20journalists%20travelling%20to%20Thailand%20to%20cover%20the%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESancho%20was%20found%20guilty%20of%20premeditated%20murder%2C%20concealing%20a%20corpse%2C%20and%20destroying%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20court%20on%20the%20nearby%20island%20of%20Koh%20Samui%2C%20where%20the%20trial%20took%20place%2C%20initially%20sentenced%20him%20to%20death%20for%20murder.%20However%2C%20this%20was%20reduced%20to%20life%20imprisonment%20due%20to%20his%20cooperation%20during%20the%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESancho%2C%20a%20chef%20with%20his%20own%20YouTube%20channel%2C%20was%20also%20ordered%20to%20pay%204%20million%20baht%20(%24118%2C000)%20to%20compensate%20Arrieta's%20family.%20Bussakorn%20Kaewleeled%2C%20the%20victim's%20family%20lawyer%2C%20expressed%20satisfaction%20with%20the%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20plaintiff%20is%20satisfied%20with%20the%20sentence%20because%20he%20(Sancho)%20will%20be%20put%20in%20prison%20for%20life%20and%20they%20(the%20plaintiff)%20receive%20some%20financial%20compensation%2C%26quot%3B%20Bussakorn%20told%20reporters%20outside%20the%20Koh%20Samui%20court%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20AFP%20news%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20found%20parts%20of%20Arrieta's%20body%20at%20a%20landfill%20in%20Koh%20Phangan%20in%20early%20August%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20that%20time%2C%20Sancho%20reported%20to%20the%20police%20that%20Arrieta%2C%20then%2044%2C%20was%20missing.%20After%20further%20questioning%2C%20Sancho%20confessed%20to%20the%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThai%20media%20reported%20that%20investigations%20had%20shown%20Sancho%20had%20purchased%20a%20knife%2C%20rubber%20gloves%2C%20and%20a%20bottle%20of%20cleaning%20agent%2C%20leading%20police%20to%20conclude%20the%20murder%20was%20premeditated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESancho%20later%20led%20police%20to%20seven%20locations%20around%20the%20island%20where%20he%20had%20disposed%20of%20Arrieta's%20dismembered%20body%20in%20plastic%20bags.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20stated%20that%20Sancho%20and%20Arrieta%20had%20agreed%20to%20meet%20after%20becoming%20acquainted%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20defence%20argued%20that%20Sancho%20acted%20in%20self-defence%20when%20Arrieta%20tried%20to%20force%20him%20into%20a%20sexual%20encounter.%20In%20a%20statement%20published%20by%20the%20Spanish%20newspaper%20El%20Mundo%2C%20Sancho%20said%20the%20plastic%20surgeon%20%26quot%3Btried%20to%20rape%20%5Bhim%5D.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESancho%20comes%20from%20a%20family%20of%20actors%3B%20his%20mother%20is%20actress%20Silvia%20Bronchalo%2C%20and%20his%20grandfather%20was%20the%20late%20actor%20Felix%20Angel%20Sancho%20Gracia.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724934000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fkgggoac8_daniel-sancho-bronchalo_625x300_29_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworl