hostile.%20Trying%20to%20find%20it%20on%20the%20school's%20website%20or%20in%20your%20email%20(why%20do%20schools%20send%20everything%20as%20attachments%3F!%20ugh!)%20is%20a%20nightmare%20when%20you%20need%20to%20look%20up%20whether%20your%20kids%20have%20school%20on%20President's%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you've%20never%20been%20caught%20slackjawed%20when%20your%20child%20informs%20you%20that%20they%20have%20a%20half%20day%20that%20day%2C%20I%20salute%20you.%20The%20rest%20of%20us%2C%20we're%20out%20here%20sweating%20and%20scrambling%20and%20dedicating%2030%25%20of%20our%20brain%20cells%20to%20juggling%20a%20school%20calendar%20along%20with%20the%20after-school%20activities%20calendar%2C%20the%20endless%20forms%20that%20need%20to%20be%20filled%2C%20making%20sure%20that%20the%20yellow%20shirt%20is%20washed%20before%20the%20color%20day%20of%20Spirit%20Week.%20(This%20work%2C%20of%20course%2C%20is%20more%20often%20done%20by%20moms).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20understand%20that%20public%20schools%20are%20in%20the%20business%20of%20educating%2C%20not%20web%20design.%20Revamping%20the%20clunky%20calendar%20formats%20and%20websites%20are%20not%20a%20top%20funding%20priority.%20So%20I'm%20ready%20to%20roll%20up%20my%20sleeves%20and%20do%20it%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20sort%20of.%20I%20want%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-use-chatgpt-at-work-job-save-time-ai-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20do%20this%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20inspired%20last%20week%20by%20Dan%20Seifert%2C%20a%20former%20reporter%20at%20The%20Verge%20and%20now%20Google%20employee%2C%20who%20posted%20on%20Threads%20about%20how%20he%20used%20AI%20to%20take%20the%20Word%20doc%20with%20his%20child's%20school%20calendar%20and%20pop%20those%20dates%20into%20his%20Google%20cal%20with%20just%20a%20few%20moves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads.net%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-text-post-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads.net%2F%40danseifert%2Fpost%2FC_B9bBnv2Fk%5C%22%20data-text-post-version%3D%5C%220%5C%22%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads.net%2F%40danseifert%2Fpost%2FC_B9bBnv2Fk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20Post%20by%20%40danseifert%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20View%20on%20Threads%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20to%20me%2C%20was%20the%20dream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeifert%20described%20how%20he%20did%20this%20using%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-google-pixel-phone%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Pixel%3C%2Fa%3E%20phone.%20I%20reached%20out%20to%20Seifert%2C%20but%20he%20wasn't%20authorized%20to%20speak%20on%20the%20record%20in%20detail%20about%20this.%20Since%20I%20don't%20have%20a%20Pixel%2C%20his%20exact%20method%20wasn't%20going%20to%20work%20for%20me%2C%20but%20I%20am%20grateful%20for%20his%20inspiration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20about%20two%20hours%2C%20three%20separate%20LLMs%20(ChatGPT%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-gemini-bard%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGemini%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Claude)%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20frustration%2C%20I%20finally%20was%20able%20to%20get%20this%20to%20work.%20To%20test%20further%2C%20I%20tried%20out%20my%20methods%20for%20two%20other%20friends%20and%20their%20school%20calendars%20and%20got%20it%20to%20work%20for%20them%2C%20too.%20Some%20tweaking%20was%20required%20to%20deal%20with%20one%20weirdly%20formatted%20calendar%2C%20but%20I%20was%20still%20able%20to%20get%20it%20there.%20Triumph!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20I%20have%20suffered%2C%20I%20am%20pleased%20to%20spare%20you%20all%20and%20tell%20you%20how%20I%20did%20it%20so%20you%20can%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22037236f3-c580-4600-99c4-3d8f8f70b15b%5C%22%3EA%20few%20caveats%3A%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20am%20not%20a%20master%20of%20AI%20by%20any%20means%2C%20and%20there%20may%20be%20a%20much%20better%20way%20to%20do%20this.%20I'm%20happy%20to%20hear%20any%20suggestions%20you%20might%20have%20to%20streamline%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20was%20using%20the%20free%20versions%20of%20these%20LLMs%3B%20its%20possible%20that%20the%20more%20powerful%20paid%20versions%20could%20do%20this%20better.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2243dfa2c7-df5b-4b8c-995d-61afe4adb3aa%5C%22%3EHere%20were%20my%20steps%3A%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStep%201%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Get%20your%20school%20calendar.%20This%20can%20be%20a%20PDF%2C%20a%20screenshot%20of%20the%20calendar%2C%20or%20a%20copy-and-paste%20of%20all%20the%20text%20from%20a%20written%20document.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStep%202.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Use%20ChatGPT%20to%20read%20the%20PDF%20or%20image%20and%20turn%20it%20into%20plain%20text.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPrompt%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20a%20PDF%20of%20a%20school%20calendar%20with%20a%20list%20of%20dates.%20Please%20take%20this%20PDF%20and%20turn%20it%20into%20a%20text%20list%20of%20all%20the%20dates%20and%20their%20descriptions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStep%202.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Turn%20that%20plain%20text%20into%20a%20Google%20Calendar-friendly%20CSV%20file.%20This%20might%20take%20a%20few%20tries%20to%20massage%20it%20to%20get%20it%20in%20the%20exact%20right%20format%20for%20Google%20Cal.%20You%20might%20have%20to%20ask%20it%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20dates%20go%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPrompt%3A%20%26quot%3BCan%20you%20take%20that%20list%20and%20turn%20it%20into%20a%20CSV%20file%20with%20the%20dates%20in%20the%20YYYY-MM-DD%20format%20that's%20ready%20to%20import%20into%20Google%20Calendar%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStep%203.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Download%20the%20.txt%20version%20it%20provides%2C%20or%20copy%20and%20paste%20it%20into%20a%20text%20editor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETip%3A%20I%20found%20that%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FClaude.ai%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EClaude.ai%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20was%20better%20at%20this%20step%20than%20ChatGPT%20or%20Gemini.%20Claude%20could%20also%20create%20a%20downloadable%20version%2C%20which%20saved%20me%20a%20step%20of%20having%20to%20paste%20and%20save%20it%20myself.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStep%204.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20Google%20Calendar%2C%20create%20a%20new%20calendar%20with%20the%20%2B%20sign%20next%20to%20%26quot%3BOther%20calendars%26quot%3B%20(located%20in%20the%20left%20rail%20if%20you're%20on%20a%20desktop).%20Name%20it%20%26quot%3BSchool%20calendar%26quot%3B%20or%20whatever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETip%3A%20Share%20it%20with%20your%20partner%20so%20they%20can%20never%20claim%20they%20didn't%20know%20that%20random%20Tuesday%20was%20closed%20for%20%26quot%3BTeacher%20Development%20Day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStep%205.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Import%20your%20.txt%20file%20into%20Google%20Calendar.%20Go%20to%20Settings%20%3E%20Import%20%26amp%3B%20export%20%3E%20Import.%20Upload%20the%20file%20from%20your%20computer%20and%20select%20the%20calendar%20for%20import.%20If%20it%20gives%20an%20error%20message%20or%20says%200%20events%20added%2C%20you'll%20need%20to%20go%20back%20and%20fiddle%20with%20the%20formatting%20again%20from%20Step%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStep%206.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Be%20satisfied%20with%20yourself%20for%20being%20a%20master%20of%20efficiency.%20Congratulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225122d1a6-68cf-4e55-8474-1032bfecd987%5C%22%3EA%20few%20things%20you%20should%20know%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20wasn't%20as%20simple%20as%20I%20hoped.%20It%20took%20a%20little%20trial%20and%20error%2C%20and%20some%20of%20the%20LLMs%20couldn't%20do%20all%20of%20the%20steps%20on%20their%20own%2C%20which%20is%20of%20course%2C%20incredibly%20frustrating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20some%20reason%2C%20Gemini%20fared%20the%20worst%20of%20all%20of%20these%20at%20being%20able%20to%20do%20this.%20It%20also%20strangely%20gave%20me%20the%20wrong%20information%20about%20how%20to%20use%20Google%20products.%20For%20example%2C%20it%20told%20me%20at%20first%20it%20could%20read%20a%20PDF%20in%20my%20Google%20Drive%2C%20but%20then%20later%20told%20me%20it%20wasn't%20allowed%20to%20access%20Google%20Drive%20files.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20gave%20me%20bad%20instructions%20when%20I%20asked%20about%20how%20to%20add%20all%20these%20dates%20to%20Google%20Calendar%20(it%20suggested%20creating%20a%20single%20event%20and%20putting%20all%20the%20plain%20text%20in%20the%20description)%20instead%20of%20telling%20me%20how%20to%20import%20a%20file.%20I%20assumed%20that%20Google's%20Gemini%20would%20be%20better%20at%20helping%20with%20other%20Google%20products%2C%20but%20not%20quite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20imagine%20that%20Google%20(and%20others)%20will%20be%20making%20this%20workflow%20much%20easier%20very%20soon.%20This%20seems%20like%20the%20ideal%20use%20of%20AI%20as%20a%20productivity%20tool%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20a%20document%20in%20my%20Gmail%20or%20Drive%20with%20a%20list%20of%20dates.%20Please%20add%20all%20those%20dates%20to%20my%20calendar.%26quot%3B%20That's%20the%20magic%20that%20you%20want%20AI%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20yes%2C%20there%20are%20companies%20out%20there%20specifically%20working%20to%20help%20families%20manage%20this%20annoying%20task%20of%20managing%20the%20calendar.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohai.ai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOhai%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20app%20aimed%20at%20moms%20that%20acts%20as%20an%20assistant%20that%20can%20help%20with%20calendar%20management%20as%20well%20as%20other%20tasks%20(it's%20%2427%20a%20month%20and%20looks%20promising%2C%20although%20I%20haven't%20tested%20it%20myself).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.skylightframe.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Skylight%20calendar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20%24300%20digital%20calendar%20touch%20screen%20device%20(there's%20also%20a%20%24600%20larger%20wall%20size%20coming%20out%20this%20fall).%20My%20editor%2C%20Hayley%20Peterson%2C%20just%20got%20one%20for%20her%20family%20and%20says%20she%20loves%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20have%20a%20feeling%20that%20all%20this%20hassle%20will%20be%20moot%20by%20the%20start%20of%20the%20next%20school%20year.%20When%20the%20new%20iPhones%20have%20their%20fancy%20new%20Apple%20Intelligence%20and%20other%20AI%20models%20have%20grown%20even%20more%20powerful%2C%20I%20imagine%20that%20all%20this%20will%20be%20as%20simple%20as%20a%20few%20taps%20on%20our%20phones%2C%20with%20no%20hassle%20of%20importing%20a%20.txt%20file%20(shudder).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%20people%20are%20worried%20that%20AI%20might%20replace%20our%20jobs%2C%20swarm%20us%20with%20misinformation%2C%20and%20harm%20us%20in%20ways%20we%20haven't%20even%20predicted%20yet.%20I%20am%20worried%2C%20too.%20I%20don't%20use%20AI%20much%20at%20work%20(I%20wrote%20all%20these%20words%20with%20my%20own%20two%20fingers).%20But%20I%20am%20also%20really%2C%20really%20happy%20to%20make%20this%20tool%20actually%20do%20something%20that%20improves%20my%20life%20in%20this%20small%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanage-school-calendar-pdf-with-ai-google-chatgpt-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724933702000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66cf9511397a168972024ca4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanage-school-calendar-pdf-with-ai-google-chatgpt-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20used%20ChatGPT%20to%20turn%20my%20kid's%20school%20calendar%20from%20a%20crummy%20PDF%20into%20Google%20events%2C%20eliminating%