n%20oil%20tycoon%20in%20his%20forties.%3Cp%3EEndeavor%20Energy%20Resources%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAutry%20Stephens%20sold%20his%20oil%20company%20for%20%2426%20billion%20but%20died%20before%20the%20deal%20was%20completed.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Texan%20farm%20boy%20became%20an%20oil%20tycoon%20by%20betting%20big%2C%20minimizing%20costs%2C%20and%20working%20tirelessly.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHere's%20a%20closer%20look%20at%20Stephens'%20life%20and%20the%20monster%20deal%20he%20struck%20months%20before%20his%20death.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAutry%20Stephens%20spent%2045%20years%20building%20one%20of%20the%20nation's%20largest%20private%20oil%20producers%20and%20finally%20agreed%20to%20sell%20it%20for%20%2426%20billion%20this%20year%20%E2%80%94%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-deals-autry-stephens-endeavor-diamondback-energy-billionaires-rich-list-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edied%20before%20the%20deal%20closed%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Texas%20farm%20boy%20became%20an%20oil%20tycoon%20by%20taking%20big%20risks%2C%20pinching%20pennies%2C%20hustling%20hard%2C%20and%20finding%20ways%20to%20survive%20when%20others%20failed.%20Here's%20the%20story%20of%20his%20life%20and%20his%20last%20big%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2236c5efde-9e9d-4363-a20b-58af577cef02%5C%22%3EDrilling%20down%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStephens%20was%20born%20in%201938%2C%20raised%20on%20a%20fruit-and-peanut%20farm%20in%20the%20Texas%20town%20of%20DeLeon%2C%20and%20studied%20petroleum%20engineering%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Texas%20at%20Austin's%20engineering%20school%2C%20according%20to%20a%20profile%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20first%20job%20after%20graduating%20was%20at%20Humble%20Oil%2C%20an%20ExxonMobil%20predecessor.%20He%20promptly%20took%20two%20years%20out%20to%20join%20the%20US%20Army%20Corps%20of%20Engineers%20as%20a%20lieutenant%20and%20platoon%20leader%20in%20charge%20of%20installing%20pipelines%20before%20rejoining%20Humble%20for%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20next%20gig%20was%20as%20an%20appraisal%20engineer%20for%20a%20bank%20in%20Midland%2C%20Texas.%20Next%2C%20he%20struck%20out%20on%20his%20own%20as%20an%20independent%20consulting%20engineer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStephens%20was%20in%20his%20forties%20by%20the%20time%20he%20drilled%20his%20first%20well%20in%201979.%20He%20plowed%20his%20life%20savings%20into%20the%20prospect%2C%20which%20%26quot%3Bwasn't%20very%20smart%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%2045%20years%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frise-fall-of-energy-titan-aubrey-mcclendon-2016-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewildcatter%3C%2Fa%3E%20established%20Big%20Dog%20Drilling%20Company%2C%20which%20had%20a%20single%20rig%20at%20first%2C%20and%20then%20Endeavor%20Energy%20Resources.%20He%20built%20his%20business%20into%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20oil%20exploration%20and%20production%20companies%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-oil-production-boom-crude-supply-wti-price-goldman-sachs-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPermian%20Basin%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20West%20Texas%20and%20New%20Mexico.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEndeavor%20now%20owns%20410%2C000%20net%20acres%20across%20multiple%20basins%2C%20boasts%20thousands%20of%20wells%2C%20and%20produces%20more%20than%20420%2C000%20gross%20operated%20barrels%20of%20oil%20equivalent%20per%20day%2C%20according%20to%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aa67b277-e6a4-4fa5-b4a7-93fd25904d00%5C%22%3EStriking%20oil%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStephens%20competed%20with%20the%20oil%20majors%20as%20an%20underdog%2C%20purchasing%20wells%20they%20deemed%20too%20costly%20to%20bring%20online.%20He%20drove%20down%20costs%20by%20drilling%20one%20well%20at%20a%20time%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flearn-from-elon-musk-vertical-integration-leadership-spacex-tesla%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuying%20or%20setting%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%20his%20own%20fracking%2C%20trucking%2C%20construction%2C%20and%20oil%20services%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20rivals%20faltered%20during%20industry%20downturns%2C%20Stephens%20bought%20cheap%20mineral%20rights%20and%20acquired%20businesses%20for%20his%20stable.%20He%20stayed%20afloat%20when%20crude%20prices%20plunged%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F2008%2F9%2Foil-to-91-as-global-economy-collapses%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2008%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-drops-to-five-year-low-2014-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2014%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20shutting%20down%20his%20rigs%2C%20flogging%20assets%2C%20and%20securing%20new%20lenders%2C%20per%20the%20Journal.%20He%20also%20issued%20long-term%20bonds%20and%20stabilized%20the%20selling%20prices%20for%20his%20oil%20using%20futures%20contracts%2C%20per%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEndeavor%20has%20been%20riding%20high%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Fus-oil-production-outlook-opec-cuts-saudi-arabia-flood-market-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20shale%20wave%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%202016%2C%20when%20it%20shifted%20its%20focus%20to%20fracking%20and%20horizontal%20drilling.%20Stephens%20told%20the%20Journal%20that%20he'd%20been%20fending%20off%20buyout%20offers%20from%20ExxonMobil%20and%20Shell%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20finally%20accepted%20a%20%2426%20billion%20deal%20for%20Endeavor%20from%20Diamondback%20Energy%20in%20February.%20One%20big%20reason%20was%20that%20he'd%20been%20diagnosed%20with%20cancer%2C%20and%20the%20disease%20was%20taking%20a%20physical%20toll%20on%20him%2C%20he%20told%20the%20Journal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b62e82ef-8d34-46c7-8e7e-b3a8b1bf3940%5C%22%3EWork%2