20more%20technology%20its%20antiquated%20military%20badly%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNorth%20Korea's%20air%20force%2C%20for%20example%2C%20is%20woefully%20small%20and%20desperately%20in%20need%20of%20more%20modern%20aircraft%20to%20be%20a%20viable%20fighting%20force%2C%26quot%3B%20Parakilas%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2249fd8307-e3e8-4e1c-862e-222e575f2a77%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20precarious%20alliance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20both%20leaders%20are%20reaping%20short-term%20gains%2C%20there%20are%20problems%20on%20the%20horizon%20that%20could%20derail%20the%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20North%20Korea%20is%20delivering%20the%20shells%20Russia%20needs%20in%20volume%2C%20their%20quality%20is%20often%20shoddy%2C%20and%20there%20are%20doubts%20over%20North%20Korea's%20capacity%20to%20keep%20up%20the%20deliveries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUkrainian%20sources%20suggest%20that%20the%20shells%20Russia%20has%20received%20from%20the%20DPRK%20are%20dated%20%E2%80%94%20some%20allegedly%20manufactured%20in%20the%201970s%20and%201980s%20%E2%80%94%20and%20are%20of%20poor%20quality%2C%20having%20a%20high%20rate%20of%20failure%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Daniel%20Salisbury%2C%20an%20expert%20on%20arms%20proliferation%20at%20King's%20College%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Putin's%20decision%20to%20draw%20closer%20to%20Kim%20is%20endangering%20his%20relationship%20with%20his%20most%20important%20ally%2C%20the%20Chinese%20leader%20Xi%20Jinping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fputin-kim-jong-un-getting-closer-china-reason-to-worry-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnalysts%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20June%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Xi%20is%20watching%20the%20security%20alliance%20between%20Russia%20and%20North%20Korea%20warily%2C%20concerned%20that%20it%20could%20upset%20the%20balance%20of%20power%20in%20east%20Asia%20and%20spark%20a%20conflict%20China%20would%20sooner%20avoid.%3C%2Fp%3E