%3EBut%20there%20were%20magical%20moments%2C%20too.%20I%20held%20my%20breath%20as%20they%20tried%20to%20take%20their%20first%20steps%20and%20cried%20with%20them%20as%20they%20failed%20repeatedly.%20When%20I%20brought%20one%20of%20them%20to%20preschool%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20I%20cried%20as%20the%20teacher%20had%20to%20pull%20him%20off%20from%20around%20my%20neck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20memories%20from%20being%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstay-at-home-dad-breadwinner-mom-double-standards-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estay-at-home%20dad%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20be%20the%20memories%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20my%20mind%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bfaa0309-e64f-41e3-85de-cfe3a095e683%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDespite%20the%20misconceptions%2C%20being%20a%20stay-at-home%20dad%20has%20been%20worth%20it%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20even%20in%20society%20today%2C%20men%20staying%20home%20and%20raising%20their%20children%20are%20viewed%20differently%20than%20women%20staying%20home%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%20some%20people%20consider%20me%20%26quot%3Bless%20manly%26quot%3B%20for%20staying%20home%20with%20the%20kids.%20I%20also%20know%20some%20people%20think%20of%20me%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bfreeloader%26quot%3B%20because%20my%20wife%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbreadwinner-in-marriage-stay-at-home-dad-advice-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebreadwinner%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I'd%20be%20lying%20if%20I%20told%20you%20those%20comments%20didn't%20bother%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20not%20true%2C%20and%20you%20would%20never%20think%20those%20things%20about%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstay-at-home-mom-qualities-office-job-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estay-at-home%20mom%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20can%20get%20frustrating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20wouldn't%20exchange%