-green-energy-powered-data-centres-for-ai-in-jamnagar-124082900818_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Freliance-announces-green-energy-powered-data-centres-for-ai-in-jamnagar-124082900818_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Unified%20Pension%20Scheme%3A%20A%20Mix%20Of%20New%20And%20Old%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Fgws%2Fms%2Fwhat-is-unified-pension-scheme%2Fassets%2F4.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Modi%20government's%20decision%20to%20introduce%20an%20assured%20pension%20for%20central%20government%20employees%20reflects%20political%20pragmatism%20over%20strict%20fiscal%20calculations.%20On%20August%2024%2C%20the%20Union%20Cabinet%20approved%20the%20new%20Unified%20Pension%20Scheme%20(UPS)%20for%202.3%20million%20central%20government%20employees%20across%20India.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20UPS%20combines%20elements%20of%20both%20the%20New%20Pension%20Scheme%20(NPS)%20and%20the%20Old%20Pension%20Scheme%20(OPS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20introducing%20the%20UPS%2C%20the%20central%20government%20aims%20to%20address%20the%20dissatisfaction%20among%20employees%20with%20the%20NPS.%20Following%20persistent%20demands%20to%20revert%20to%20the%20OPS%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20established%20a%20committee%20under%20the%20chairmanship%20of%20then%20Finance%20Secretary%20(now%20Cabinet%20Secretary-designate)%20TV%20Somanathan%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UPS%20guarantees%20a%20pension%20of%2050%25%20of%20the%20basic%20salary%20for%20employees%20who%20joined%20the%20service%20after%20January%201%2C%202004.%20Employees%20opting%20for%20the%20UPS%20will%20be%20eligible%20for%20this%20guaranteed%20pension%20after%2025%20years%20of%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20scheme%20will%20take%20effect%20on%20April%201%2C%202025%2C%20with%20benefits%20applicable%20to%20those%20retiring%20by%20March%2031%2C%202025%2C%20including%20the%20payment%20of%20any%20arrears.%20Employees%20will%20have%20the%20option%20to%20choose%20between%20the%20UPS%20and%20the%20NPS%20starting%20from%20the%20upcoming%20financial%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Trio%3A%20UPS-NPS-OPS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UPS%20offers%20a%20guaranteed%2050%25%20pension%2C%20dearness%20relief%2C%20family%20pension%2C%20an%20increased%20government%20contribution%20from%2014%25%20to%2018.5%25%2C%20and%20additional%20lump-sum%20payments%20on%20retirement.%20The%20new%20scheme%20will%20provide%20a%20minimum%20pension%20of%20Rs%2010%2C000%20per%20month%2C%20which%20will%20be%20adjusted%20for%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20existing%20NPS%2C%20which%20requires%20a%2010%25%20contribution%20from%20the%20employee's%20basic%20salary%20with%20the%20government%20contributing%2014%25%2C%20will%20remain%20an%20option.%20Unlike%20the%20OPS%2C%20where%20employees%20did%20not%20contribute%2C%20the%20UPS%20is%20a%20contributory%20pension%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntroduced%20by%20the%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20government%20to%20reform%20India's%20pension%20policies%20and%20address%20fiscal%20health%2C%20the%20NPS%20replaced%20the%20OPS%20on%20January%201%2C%202004.%20Rambir%20Dalal%2C%20former%20PF%20Commissioner%20and%20currently%20managing%20partner%20at%20Peoplescient%20Consulting%20LLP%2C%20notes%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20good%20pension%20system%20should%20ensure%20adequacy%20of%20benefits%2C%20be%20fiscally%20sustainable%2C%20and%20be%20transparent%20for%20beneficiaries.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDalal%20adds%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20UPS%20meets%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20guaranteed%20pension%20and%20mitigates%20the%20risks%20associated%20with%20investment%20and%20insufficient%20corpus%20accumulation%20in%20the%20NPS.%26quot%3B%20He%20further%20explains%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20increases%20pension%20coverage%20and%20flexibility%20by%20reducing%20the%20minimum%20service%20eligibility%2C%20allowing%20government%20employees%20to%20switch%20careers%20after%2010%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitical%20Compulsions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20party%20promised%20a%20return%20to%20the%20OPS%20during%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20and%20Rajasthan%20over%20the%20past%20two%20years.%20Congress%20governments%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20(2023)%2C%20Rajasthan%20(2022)%2C%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20(2022)%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20AAP%20government%20in%20Punjab%20(2022)%2C%20have%20reinstated%20the%20OPS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20Congress's%20losses%20in%20the%202023%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20current%20BJP%20state%20governments%20in%20both%20states%20continue%20with%20the%20OPS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20victory%20for%20the%20people%20of%20India.%20We%20should%20not%20forget%20that%20it%20was%20Congress%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20followed%20by%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20that%20restored%20the%20OPS%20in%20response%20to%20government%20employees'%20demands%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Pranav%20Jha%2C%20AICC%20Secretary%20attached%20to%20the%20Congress%20President's%20office.%3Cbr%3E%5CnHe%20adds%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20subdued%20Modi%20government%2C%20following%20the%20June%204%20drubbing%2C%20has%20been%20compelled%20to%20reconsider%20its%20stance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20OPS%20was%20not%20mentioned%20in%20the%20Congress%20Lok%20Sabha%20manifesto.%20While%20the%20UPS%20is%20not%20identical%20to%20the%20OPS%2C%20its%20benefits%20for%20retiring%20employees%20are%20seen%20as%20similar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20scheme%20could%20potentially%20serve%20as%20a%20template%20for%20extending%20benefits%20to%20state%20governments%20and%20public%20sector%20employees%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20new%20scheme%20may%20help%20the%20government%20regain%20the%20support%20of%20government%20employees%2C%20a%20vocal%20political%20constituency.%20The%20results%20of%20the%20general%20election%20and%20the%20challenge%20from%20the%20Opposition%20in%20upcoming%20Assembly%20elections%20in%20Haryana%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20Jharkhand%20may%20have%20also%20influenced%20the%20government's%20decision%20to%20increase%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFinancial%20Impact%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPension%20liabilities%20for%20the%20Centre%20and%20states%20have%20significantly%20increased%20in%20recent%20years.%20In%202023-24%2C%20the%20central%20and%20state%20governments%20allocated%20Rs%202.3%20lakh%20crore%20and%20Rs%205.2%20lakh%20crore%20respectively%20for%20pensions.%20It%20is%20estimated%20that%20around%2012%25%20of%20revenue%20expenditure%20in%20all%20states%20and%20UTs%20is%20allocated%20to%20pensions%2C%20with%20higher%20percentages%20in%20states%20with%20the%20OPS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20asserts%20that%20the%20UPS%20is%20fiscally%20prudent.%20The%20expenditure%20on%20arrears%20will%20be%20Rs%20800%20crore%20in%20the%20first%20year%2C%20with%20an%20estimated%20total%20cost%20of%20Rs%206%2C250%20crore.%20%26quot%3BThe%20UPS%20remains%20within%20the%20framework%20of%20a%20contributory%20funded%20scheme%2C%20unlike%20the%20OPS%2C%20which%20is%20unfunded%20and%20non-contributory%2C%26quot%3B%20Somanathan%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20major%20financial%20impact%20of%20the%20UPS%20will%20stem%20from%20the%20increased%20government%20contribution%20-%20from%2014%25%20to%2018.5%25%20of%20the%20basic%20and%20dearness%20allowance%20(DA).%20%26quot%3BWhile%20this%20will%20create%20additional%20short-term%20financial%20burdens%2C%20the%20UPS%20will%20be%20more%20fiscally%20sustainable%20than%20the%20OPS%20in%20the%20long%20run.%20In%20a%20growing%20economy%2C%20the%20availability%20of%20long-term%20pension%20funds%20can%20support%20the%20development%20of%20physical%20infrastructure%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dalal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UPS%20is%20designed%20for%20a%20relatively%20small%20number%20of%20government%20employees%2C%20with%20costs%20borne%20by%20all%20taxpayers%2C%20including%20those%20in%20the%20private%20sector%20who%20lack%20job%20and%20pension%20security.%20It%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20how%20the%20government%20will%20balance%20the%20demands%20of%20political%20economy%20with%20these%20financial%20considerations.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724932380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Fgws%2Fms%2Fwhat-is-unified-pension-scheme%2Fassets%2F4.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Funified-pension-scheme-a-mix-of-new-and-old-6445251%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22By%20introducing%20the%20UPS%2C%20the%20central%20government%20aims%20to%20address%20the%20dissatisfaction%20among%20employees%20with%20the%20NPS.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Funified-pension-scheme-a-mix-of-new-and-old-6445251%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BFirst%20Day%20They%20Didn't%20Speak%26quot%3B%3A%20How%20Rohit%2C%20Hardik%20Buried%20Their%20Differences%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%2017th%20edition%20of%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20was%20marred%20by%20controversy%20surrounding%20the%20captaincy%20change%20at%20Mumbai%20Indians%20(MI).%20The%20five-time%20champions%20made%20a%20big%20call%20heading%20into%20IPL%202024%2C%20replacing%20long-serving%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hardik%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64177-hardik-himanshu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20the%20franchise%20bringing%20him%20back%20from%20Gujarat%20Titans%20(GT)%20as%20part%20of%20an%20all%20cash%20deal.%20This%20led%20to%20further%20speculations%20of%20a%20rift%20between%20Rohit%20and%20Hardik.%20This%20alleged%20bad%20blood%20between%20the%20two%20led%20to%20MI%20finishing%20at%20the%20bottom%20spot%20in%20the%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tension%20between%20the%20two%20continued%20in%20the%20lead%20up%20to%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%20but%20Rohit%20and%20Hardik%20eventually%20sort%20out%20their%20differences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20veteran%20journalist%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Vimal%20Kumar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F111033-vimal-kumar-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVimal%20Kumar%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20made%20a%20big%20revelation%20regarding%20the%20relationship%20between%20Rohit%20and%20Hardik%20during%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20recent%20interaction%2C%20Vimal%20revealed%20that%20the%20two%20didn't%20spoke%20to%20each%20other%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20practice.%20However%2C%20he%20added%20that%20Rohit%20and%20Hardik%20had%20a%20heart-to-heart%20conversation%20on%20the%20second%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20went%20to%20the%20nets%2C%20I%20noticed%20what%20was%20going%20on%20between%20Hardik%20and%20Rohit.%20On%20the%20first%20day%2C%20they%20didn't%20speak%20and%20were%20away%20from%20each%20other.%20But%20by%20the%20second%20day%2C%20I%20saw%20them%20come%20over%2C%20one%20after%20the%20other%2C%20and%20sit%20together%20in%20a%20corner%2C%20talking%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20That%20moment%20for%20me%20defined%20this%20team.%20There%20was%20no%20camera%20there%3B%20nothing.%20The%20way%20Rohit%20and%20Hardik%20were%20talking%2C%20I%20was%20like%20'what%20am%20I%20watching%3F'%2C%26quot%3B%20Vimal%20said%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.