s%20Father%3A%20Yes%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaller%3A%20The%20matter%20is%20that%20your%20daughter%20has%20probably%20died%20by%20suicide.%20She%20is%20dead%2C%20police%20are%20here%2C%20we%20are%20all%20here%2C%20please%20come%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVictim's%20Father%3A%20We%20are%20coming%2C%20right%20away%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVictim's%20Mother%20(screams%20in%20the%20background)%3A%20My%20daughter%20is%20no%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hospital%20administration's%20communication%20with%20the%20victim's%20parents%20is%20one%20aspect%20of%20this%20horrifying%20incident%20that%20has%20repeatedly%20come%20under%20scrutiny%20in%20both%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20In%20their%20petition%20in%20the%20high%20court%2C%20the%20parents%20said%20they%20were%20made%20to%20wait%20for%20three%20hours.%20They%20suspect%20that%20this%20delay%20was%20intentional.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKolkata%20Police%2C%20however%2C%20has%20contested%20this.%20Their%20timeline%20claims%20that%20the%20parents%20reached%20the%20hospital%20at%201%20pm%20and%20they%20were%20taken%20to%20the%20seminar%20hall%2C%20where%20the%20body%20was%20found%2C%2010%20minutes%20later.%20The%20courts%20have%20also%20questioned%20why%20the%20hospital%20administration%2C%20led%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-doctor-rape-murder-rg-kar-medical-college-principal-should-have-top-courts-fresh-fire-in-kolkata-rape-murder-6393611%5C%22%3Ethen%20principal%20Dr%20Sandip%20Ghosh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20did%20not%20file%20a%20formal%20police%20complaint%20and%20the%20cops%20had%20to%20register%20an%20unnatural%20death%20case.%20An%20FIR%20was%20filed%20only%20late%20at%20night%20after%20the%20victim's%20father%20filed%20a%20formal%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-rape-murder-rg-kar-she-was-only-draped-in-bedsheet-father-of-kolkata-rape-murder-victim-6364313%5C%22%3E