Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Freliance-retail-targets-doubling-business-in-3-4-years-says-isha-ambani-124082900842_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Freliance-retail-targets-doubling-business-in-3-4-years-says-isha-ambani-124082900842_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Freliance-retail-targets-doubling-business-in-3-4-years-says-isha-ambani-124082900842_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan%20Drop%20Shaheen%20Afridi%20For%202nd%20Bangladesh%20Test%2C%20This%20Is%20The%20Reason%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20facing%20criticism%20for%20heavy%20defeat%20in%20the%20series-opener%2C%20Pakistan%20on%20Thursday%20dropped%20left-arm%20fast%20bowler%20Shaheen%20Shah%20Afridi%20from%20the%20must-win%20second%20Test%20against%20Bangladesh.%20Pakistan's%20team%20combination%2C%20in%20which%20they%20fielded%20four%20pacers%2C%20also%20invited%20sharp%20criticism%20from%20former%20players%2C%20who%20felt%20that%20playing%20with%20two%20spinners%20was%20a%20better%20option.%20Head%20coach%20Jason%20Gillispie%20said%20Shaheen%20understands%20the%20%26quot%3Bsituation%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20break%20will%20give%20him%20quality%20time%20with%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20a%20good%20conversation%20with%20him%20and%20he%20fully%20understands%20we%20are%20looking%20at%20the%20best%20combination%20for%20this%20game%20and%20the%20last%20few%20weeks%20have%20been%20interesting%20for%20him%20with%20fatherhood%20and%20other%20things%2C%20this%20break%20will%20allow%20him%20to%20spend%20time%20with%20his%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20Gillispie%20said%20during%20the%20pre-match%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Australian%20pacer%20said%20Shaheen%20is%20working%20with%20Azhar%20Mahmood%20to%20be%20more%20effective%20and%20the%20management%20certainly%20wants%20to%20see%20him%20at%20his%20very%20best%20as%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20cricket%20coming%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRight%20now%20we%20feel%20we%20have%20all%20bases%20covered%20in%20our%20bowling%20attack%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShaheen%20has%20played%20just%20six%20Tests%20since%20July%202022%2C%20owing%20to%20a%20knee%20injury.%20He%20was%20rested%20for%20the%20final%20Test%20against%20Australia%20at%20Sydney%20in%20January%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGillispie%20also%20confirmed%20that%20all%20rounder%20Aamer%20Jamal%20was%20still%20not%20fit%20to%20play%20for%20Pakistan%20and%20was%20ruled%20out%20of%20the%20match.%20He%20also%20stressed%20on%20the%20need%20for%20the%20Pakistan%20team%20to%20make%20better%20decisions%20over%20slow%20over%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20aside%20including%20allowances%20for%20weather%20and%20breaks%2C%20we%20need%20to%20be%20better%20to%20get%20through%20overs%20better.%26quot%3B%20Pakistan%20were%20fined%2030%20percent%20of%20match%20fees%20and%20docked%20points%20in%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20for%20slow%20over%20rates%20in%20the%20first%20Test%20that%20it%20lost%20by%2010-wickets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can%20control%20our%20energy%20levels%20to%20make%20sure%20we%20are%20going%20through%20our%20overs%20quickly.%26quot%3B%20Gillispie%20said%20he%20was%20pleased%20with%20the%20positive%20intent%20shown%20by%20the%20team%20in%20the%20first%20Test%20with%20a%20bold%20declaration%20in%20the%20first%20innings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%2C%20Bangladesh%20played%20better%20cricket%20and%20won.%20There%20is%20nothing%20we%20can%20do%20about%20it%20now%20but%20we%20have%20to%20learn%20from%20our%20mistakes%20and%20hopefully%20apply%20those%20learnings%20in%20the%20second%20test.%26quot%3B%20He%20also%20said%20that%20players%20would%20have%20to%20take%20individual%20and%20collective%20responsibility%20to%20go%20out%20there%20and%20play%20positively%20an