Cn%3Cp%3EA%20high%20throughput%20satellite%20is%20a%20communications%20satellite%20that%20can%20send%20data%20at%20much%20higher%20rates%20than%20traditional%20satellites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20will%20not%20only%20provide%20satellite-based%20internet%20connectivity%2C%20but%20a%20part%20of%20fifth%20of%20the%20capacity%20is%20being%20reserved%20for%20providing%20in-flight%20internet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConnecting%20remote%20locations%20is%20one%20big%20objective%20of%20global%20satellite%20communications%20giant%20Viasat%20Inc.%20It%20already%20has%20a%20big%20presence%20as%20it%20provides%20reliable%20connectivity%20to%20the%20Indian%20armed%20forces%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20big%20gap%20in%20India%2C%20however%2C%20is%20the%20absence%20of%20in-flight%20Internet.%20Viasat%20and%20ISRO%20hope%20to%20bridge%20that%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BISRO's%20GSAT-20%20satellite%20will%20help%20give%20in-flight%20internet%20connectivity%20and%20Viasat%20looks%20to%20cooperate%20in%20this%20win-win%20combination%2C%26quot%3B%20Mark%20Dankberg%2C%20chairman%20and%20CEO%20of%20Viasat%2C%20considered%20a%20global%20legend%20in%20satellite%20communications%2C%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Gautam%20Sharma%2C%20Managing%20Director%2C%20Viasat%20India%3B%20Mark%20Dankberg%2C%20Chairman%20and%20CEO%2C%20Viasat%2C%20and%20K%20Guru%20Gowrappan%2C%20President%2C%20Viasat%20USA%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Gautam%20Sharma%2C%20Managing%20Director%2C%20Viasat%20India%3B%20Mark%20Dankberg%2C%20Chairman%20and%20CEO%2C%20Viasat%2C%20and%20K%20Guru%20Gowrappan%2C%20President%2C%20Viasat%20USA%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fg75n2d1o_viasat-officials_625x300_29_August_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGautam%20Sharma%2C%20Managing%20Director%2C%20Viasat%20India%3B%20Mark%20Dankberg%2C%20Chairman%20and%20CEO%2C%20Viasat%2C%20and%20K%20Guru%20Gowrappan%2C%20President%2C%20Viasat%20USA%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20in-flight%20internet%20in%20domestic%20flights%20once%20the%20aircraft%20takes%20off.%20International%20flights%20coming%20to%20India%20announce%20and%20switch%20off%20in-flight%20internet%20when%20they%20enter%20Indian%20airspace.%20This%20is%20what%20is%20dubbed%20%26quot%3Bthe%20big%20internet%20hole%20over%20India%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReaching%20the%20unreached%20is%20a%20big%20push%20by%20Viasat%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20K%20Guru%20Gowrappan%2C%20president%2C%20Viasat.%20%26quot%3BViasat%20has%20a%20good%20legacy%20in%20India%20on%20the%20defence%20side%2C%20and%20now%20connecting%201.4%20billion%20Indians%20is%20a%20big%20opportunity%20for%20Viasat%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20getting%20ready%20to%20launch%20its%20big%20bird%20in%20the%20sky%20using%20SpaceX's%20Falcon-9%20rocket.%20India%20has%20opted%20to%20launch%20it%20from%20the%20US%20since%20the%20satellite%20weighs%204%2C700%20kg%20and%20is%20a%20shade%20heavier%20than%20what%20India's%20%26quot%3BBahubali%20rocket%26quot%3B%20Launch%20Vehicle%20Mark-3%20can%20take%20%C2%A0into%20a%20geostationary%20orbit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20a%20leading%20space%20power%20in%20the%20world.%20The%20Indian%20Navy%20depends%20on%20Viasat%20for%20communications%20through%20Viasat's%20recent%20acquisition%20of%20Inmarsat%2C%20a%20specialist%20in%20providing%20connectivity%20in%20the%20high%20seas%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Dankberg%20said.%20Viasat%20has%20a%20huge%20footprint%20in%20India%20and%20hopes%20to%20expand%20its%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConnecting%20the%20unconnected%20is%20its%20goal.%20India%20is%20known%20for%20frugal%20and%20reliable%20technology%20and%20in%20future%20Viasat%20could%20also%20make%20satellites%20in%20India%20for%20the%20world%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724929800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fk78