arlier%20this%20week%2C%20the%2038-year-old%20first-time%20MP%2C%20whose%20latest%20film%20'Emergency'%20is%20set%20to%20release%20on%20September%206%2C%20had%20suggested%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshes-not-authorised-bjp-on-kangana-ranauts-farmers-protest-remarks-6421584%5C%22%3Efarmers'%20protest%20could%20have%20led%20to%20a%20Bangladesh-like%20crisis%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheikh%20Hasina%2C%20Bangladesh's%20five-time%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20was%20forced%20to%20flee%20her%20country%20on%20August%205%20in%20the%20face%20of%20massive%20protests%20over%20job%20quotas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20disapproved%20of%20her%20statements%20and%20said%20the%20actor-turned-MP%2C%20a%20four-time%20national%20award%20winner%2C%20is%20not%20authorised%20to%20speak%20on%20policy%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mandi%20MP%2C%20a%20Padma%20Shri%20winner%2C%20also%20alleged%20the%20involvement%20of%20China%20and%20the%20US%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bconspiracy%26quot%3B%2C%20drawing%20flak%20from%20the%20Opposition%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20has%20directed%20Kangana%20Ranaut%20to%20not%20make%20any%20statement%20of%20this%20kind%20in%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ruling%20party%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20as%20her%20controversial%20remarks%20threatened%20to%20inflame%20an%20issue%20it%20has%20tried%20hard%20to%20contain%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20farmers%20from%20Haryana%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20other%20places%20had%20held%20an%20agitation%20at%20Delhi's%20borders%20for%20several%20months%20over%20the%20now-repealed%20farm%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20is%20committed%20to%20following%20the%20principles%20of%20'Sabka%20Saath%2C%20Sabka%20Vikas%2C%20Sabka%20Vishwas%20and%20Sabka%20Prayas'%20and%20social%20harmony%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E