47%20countries%20and%20425%20destinations%20en%20route.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20the%20ship%20is%20stuck%20in%20Belfast%2C%20passengers%20can%20go%20on%20board%20during%20the%20day%20but%20not%20stay%20on%20it%20overnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cruise%20line's%20CEO%2C%20Mikael%20Petterson%2C%20previously%20told%20BI%20that%20Villa%20Vie%20provided%20residents%20with%20a%20shuttle%20to%20and%20from%20the%20ship%2C%20as%20well%20as%20food%2C%20drinks%2C%20excursions%2C%20and%20lodging%20%E2%80%94%20or%20a%20per%20diem%20payment%20for%20those%20who%20%26quot%3Bchoose%20to%20do%20their%20own%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20couple%20on%20the%20ship%2C%20Johan%20Bodin%20and%20Lanette%20Canen%2C%20previously%20told%20BI%20they've%20traveled%20elsewhere%20during%20the%20delay%2C%20to%20the%20likes%20of%20Italy%2C%20Croatia%2C%20Slovenia%2C%20and%20Sweden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessinsider.com%2Fvilla-vie-residential-cruise-ship-odyssey-photos-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVilla%20Vie%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20also%20sent%20them%20on%20various%20excursions%2C%20including%20a%20trip%20to%20the%20Canary%20Islands%20and%20a%20cruise%20to%20the%20Norwegian%20fjords.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20understand%20there%20are%20hiccups%2C%26quot%3B%20Bodin%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20schmoozing%20us%20a%20bit%20to%20keep%20us%20happy.%20They're%20almost%20being%20too%20serviced-minded%20%E2%80%94%20I%20don't%20need%20to%20be%20pampered%20all%20the%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHolly%20Hennessey%2C%20from%20Florida%2C%20told%20BBC%20News%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20can%20have%20all%20of%20our%20meals%20and%20they%20even%20have%20movies%20and%20trivia%20entertainment%2C%20almost%20like%20cruising%20except%20we're%20at%20the%20dock.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Composite%20of%20the%20Theriacs'%20cabin%20with%20desk%20and%20bed.%5C%22%20charset%3D