26quot%3B%20between%20ex%20Chief%20Minister%20K%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao's%20party%20and%20the%20ruling%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reprimand%20came%20as%20a%20three-judge%20bench%20of%20Justices%20BR%20Gavai%2C%20PK%20Mishra%2C%20and%20KV%20Viswanathan%20was%20hearing%20a%20plea%20seeking%20transfer%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fsearch%3Fsearchtext%3Dcash-for-votes-revanth-reddy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2015%20cash-for-votes%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20to%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20The%20petitioners%20argued%20he%20could%20influence%20witnesses%20and%20tamper%20with%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20hearing%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20was%20told%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20publicly%20reported...%20the%20kind%20of%20statements%20he%20(the%20Chief%20Minister)%20made%20-%20that%20if%20police%20does%20anything%2C%20he%20will%20have%20them%20beaten%20up%20on%20streets...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20shocking%20claim%20aside%2C%20the%20hearing%20began%20on%20a%20positive%20note%20for%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20with%20the%20court%20indicating%20reluctance%20to%20transfer%20the%20case%20and%20expressing%C2%A0%26quot%3Bcomplete%20faith%26quot%3B%20in%20its%20state%20colleagues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20flurry%20of%20arguments%20the%20court%20said%20it%20would%20rule%20at%202%20pm.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECome%202%20pm%2C%20however%2C%20it%20was%20an%20enraged%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20assembled%20and%20red-flagged%20deep%20concern%20over%20the%20%26quot%3Bmanner%20of%20a%20statement%26quot%3B%20made%20by%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%20%26quot%3BHave%20you%20read%20what%20(he)%20said...%20just%20read...%20such%20statements%20by%20a%20Chief%20Minister%20might%20rightly%20create%20apprehension%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Gavai%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BIf%20You%20Do%20Not%20Respect%20Us...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShould%20a%20person%20holding%20a%20constitutional%20post%20make%20such%20statements%3F%20There%20should%20be%20mutual%20respect%20(between%20politicians%20and%20judiciary)...%20how%20can%20anyone%20say%20we%20pass%20orders%20for%20political%20reasons%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20do%20not%20respect%20(us)%20then%20we%20will%20send%20(your)%20trial%20elsewhere.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20highest%20court%20in%20the%20country...%20just%20yesterday%20we%20issued%20notice%20to%20Maharashtra's%20Additional%20Chief%20Secretary%20(Forest%20and%20Revenue%20Department)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20warned%20Mr%20Reddy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reference%20was%20to%20a%20notice%20demanding%20to%20know%20why%20the%20ACS%2C%20Rajesh%20Kumar%2C%20should%20not%20face%20contempt%20proceedings%20for%20suggesting%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20not%20following%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWill%20we%20pass%20our%20order%20after%20consulting%20any%20political%20party%3F%20This%20(claim)%20should%20be%20the%20basis%20for%20transfer%20of%20the%20case...%20we%20perform%20our%20duty%20according%20to%20conscience%20and%20oath...%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20raged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20finally%20adjourned%20to%20Monday%20the%20petition%20to%20shift%20the%20trial.%20%26quot%3BWe%20ae%20not%20closing%20this%20now...%20we%20always%20say%20we%20will%20not%20interfere%20in%20jurisdiction%20of%20legislature%20and%20same%20is%20expected%20of%20them%20too.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBail%20For%20K%20Kavitha%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EK%20Kavitha%20-%20the%20daughter%20of%20ex%20Telangana%20Chief%20Minister%20K%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%2C%20who%20was%20defeated%20by%20the%20Congress%20and%20Mr%20Reddy%20in%20last%20year's%20election%20-%20was%20yesterday%20granted%20bail%20by%20the%20top%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%