2C%20surpassing%20Mukesh%20Ambani.%20In%202020%2C%20Mr%20Adani%20was%20fourth%20on%20the%20list.%20Mr%20Adani's%20wealth%20has%20surged%20by%2095%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20last%20one%20year.%20His%20rise%20is%20marked%20by%20recovery%20following%20the%20Hindenburg%20report%2C%20which%20had%20raised%20significant%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRising%20like%20a%20phoenix%20after%20the%20Hindenburg%20allegations%2C%20Gautam%20Adani%20(62)%20%26amp%3B%20family%20have%20secured%20the%20top%20spot%20in%20this%20year's%20rankings%2C%20with%20a%2095%25%20increase%20in%20wealth%20compared%20to%20last%20year%2C%20bringing%20their%20total%20to%20INR%201%2C161%2C800%20Cr.%20As%20a%20self-made%20entrepreneur%2C%20Adani%20has%20recorded%20the%20highest%20wealth%20growth%20within%20the%20top%2010%20over%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20adding%20INR%201%2C021%2C600%20Cr%2C%20despite%20the%20challenges%20following%20the%20report%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Hurun%20Rich%20List%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20Adani%20Group%20companies%20saw%20a%20significant%20surge%20in%20share%20prices%20over%20the%20past%20year.%20For%20example%2C%20Adani%20Ports%20experienced%20a%2098%25%20increase%2C%20driven%20by%20improved%20utilization%20levels%20and%20the%20proposed%20acquisition%20of%20new%20ports%20and%20container%20terminals.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20energy-focused%20companies-Adani%20Energy%2C%20Adani%20Gas%2C%20Adani%20Transmission%2C%20and%20Adani%20Power-averaged%20a%2076%25%20growth%20in%20share%20price.%20Additionally%2C%20MSCI's%20decision%20to%20lift%20restrictions%20on%20Adani%20Group%20securities%20in%20its%20August%202024%20review%20indicates%20a%20return%20to%20normal%20operations%2C%20reflecting%20a%20stabilizing%20outlook%20for%20key%20stocks%20like%20Adani%20Enterprises%2C%20Adani%20Ports%2C%20and%20Ambuja%20Cements.%20This%20year%2C%20Hurun%20has%20attributed%20the%20wealth%20of%20the%20family%20trust%20and%20international%20companies%20within%20the%20promoter%20group%20to%20Gautam%20Adani%20and%20his%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ambani%2C%20with%20a%20wealth%20of%20Rs%2010.14%20lakh%20crore%2C%20secured%20the%20second%20position%20on%20the%20list.%20The%20wealth%20calculations%20presented%20are%20based%20on%20the%20snapshot%20taken%20on%20July%2031%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20highlights%20that%20the%20number%20of%20billionaires%20in%20the%20country%20has%20reached%20a%20record%20334%2C%20The%20Times%20of%20India%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-src%3D%5C%22visualisation%2F19220080%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22table%20visualization%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fvisualisation%2F19220080%2Fthumbnail%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnas%20Rahman%20Junaid%2C%20Founder%20and%20Chief%20Researcher%20of%20Hurun%20India%2C%20said%20the%20country%20is%20%26quot%3Bemerging%20as%20Asia's%20wealth%20creation%20engine!%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20stated%20that%20India%20experienced%20a%2029%25%20increase%2C%20even%20when%20China%20witnessed%20a%2025%25%20decline%20in%20its%20number%20of%20billionaires.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20Mr%20Adani%20and%20Mr%20Ambani%20on%20the%20list%20is%20HCL%20Technologies'%20Shiv%20Nadar%20and%20family%20in%20the%20third%20place%2C%20with%20a%20total%20wealth%20of%20Rs%203.14%20lakh%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20fourth%20and%20fifth%20positions%20were%20Cyrus%20S%20Poonawalla%20and%20the%20family%20of%20Serum%20Institute%20of%20India%20(SII)%20(Rs%202.89%20lakh%20crore)%20and%20Sun%20Pharmaceutical%20Industries'%20Dilip%20Shanghvi%20(Rs%202.49%20crore).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20further%20highlights%20that%20India%20produced%20a%20billionaire%20every%20five%20days%20last%20year.%20In%202023%2C%20the%20country%20had%20259%20billionaires.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hurun%20India%20Rich%20List%20has%20expanded%20considerably%2C%20with%20more%20than%201%2C500%20individuals%20possessing%20a%20net%20worth%20of%20Rs%201%2C000%20crore%20or%20more.%20It%20shows%20a%20150%25%20growth%20compared%20to%20seven%20years%20ago%2C%20Business%20Today%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20the%20list%20identifies%201%2C539%20ultra-rich%20individuals%2C%20a%20significant%20increase%20of%20220%20from%20the%20previous%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20when%20the%20list%20exceeds%201%2C500%20entrants%2C%20an%2086%25%20jump%20over%20the%20past%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20family-run%20businesses%20as%20well%20as%20startup%20founders%20to%20private%20equity%20investors%2C%20angel%20investors%2C%20next-generation%20leaders%2C%20and%20film%20stars%2C%20the%20list%20has%20a%20diverse%20range%20of%20wealth%20creators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20youngest%20billionaire%20on%20the%20list%20is%20Kaivalya%20Vohra%2C%20aged%2021.%20Vohra%20is%20the%20co-founder%20of%20Zepto%2C%20a%20%245%20billion%20startup.%20Aadit%20Palicha%2C%20another%20Zepto%20co-founder%2C%20is%20second%20youngest%20on%20the%20list%20at%2022%20years%20of%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724922000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fcpgqscug_gautam-adani_625x300_05_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgautam-adani-takes-top-spot-on-hurun-india-rich-list-replaces-mukesh-ambani-6443650%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gautam%20Adani%20and%20his%20family%20have%20secured%20the%20top%20spot%20in%20the%202024%20Hurun%20India%20Rich%20List%2C%20with%20a%20wealth%20of%20Rs%2011.6%20lakh%20crore%2C%20surpassing%20Mukesh%20Ambani.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgautam-adani-takes-top-spot-on-hurun-india-rich-list-replaces-mukesh-ambani-6443650%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22am