cial%20media%20profiles.%20His%20Facebook%20profile%20photo%2C%20uploaded%20in%202013%2C%20shows%20him%20posing%20with%20a%20camera%20and%20a%20cigarette%2C%20clean%20shaved%20and%20candid.%20He%20now%20sports%20a%20white%20beard%2C%20wears%20saffron%20and%20has%20religious%20markings%20on%20his%20forehead.%20His%20profile%20has%20several%20social%20media%20posts%20that%20point%20to%20links%20with%20ABVP%20and%20slam%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECatapulted%20to%20overnight%20fame%2C%20he%20posted%20a%20video%20statement%20on%20his%20Facebook%20profile%20yesterday.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20Balaram%20Bose.%20I%20was%20participant%20in%20this%20students'%20protest.%20I%20just%20want%20to%20appeal%20to%20you%20not%20to%20stop%20this%20movement.%20Please%20continue%20this%20'Justice%20for%20RG%20Kar'%20movement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fvideo.php%3Fheight%3D476%26href%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252Fprabir.bose%252Fvideos%252F1553909245206242%252F%26show_text%3Dfalse%26width%3D267%26t%3D0%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22267%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22476%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20people%20had%20come%20to%20know%20about%20him%20after%20a%20video%20went%20viral.%20%26quot%3BSome%20are%20projecting%20me%20as%20a%20villain%2C%20some%20as%20a%20hero.%20But%20I%20am%20just%20an%20ordinary%20man%2C%20like%20the%20thousands%20of%20people%20in%20this%20movement.%20My%20only%20message%20to%20the%20people%20is%3A%20persist%20in%20this%20movement%20for%20justice%2C%20no%20matter%20whatever%20narratives%20are%20created.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bose%20wished%20for%20the%20swift%20recovery%20of%20protesters%20as%20well%20as%20police%20personnel%20injured%20in%20Tuesday's%20clash.%20%26quot%3BBut%20remember%2C%20don't%20let%20this%20movement%20fade%20away.%20Keep%20saying%2C%20'Justice%20for%20RG%20Kar'.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20videos%20that%20went%20viral%20on%20the%20day%20of%20Nabanna%20Abhijaan%2C%20the%20'mystery%20man'%20was%20heard%20telling%20the%20media%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20(police)%20should%20wear%20bangles%20and%20sit%20at%20home.%20They%20also%20have%20mothers%20and%20sisters.%20We%20have%20come%20here%20to%20protest%20in%20demand%20of%20women's%20safety.%20We%20are%20not%20carrying%20weapons%2C%20we%20are%20only%20holding%20the%20national%20flag.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20%26quot%3Bwear%20bangles%26quot%3B%20prompted%20a%20wave%20of%20criticism%2C%20with%20many%20flagging%20how%20such%20gendered%20expressions%20can%20find%20a%20place%20in%20a%20movement%20for%20women's%20safety.%20Others%20defended%20him%2C%20saying%20that%20he%20had%20at%20least%20stepped%20out%20for%20the%20cause%20and%20braved%20water%20cannons%20and%20teargas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20asked%20what%20he%20was%20doing%20at%20a%20students'%20protest.%20Responding%20to%20this%2C%20Mr%20Bose%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20protest%20was%20announced%20by%20students%20and%20they%20said%20one%20person%20from%20each%20home%20must%20join.%20I%20have%20women%20at%20home%2C%20in%20my%20family.%20And%20I%20am%20concerned%20about%20their%20safety.%20So%20I%20felt%20I%20must%20join%20this%20protest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Kolkata%3A%20Balram%20Bose%2C%20who%20took%20part%20in%20the%20'Nabanna%20Abhiyan'%20march%20yesterday%2C%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20agitation%20was%20called%20by%20students%20but%20it%20was%20said%20that%20one%20individual%20from%20every%20household%20should%20join%20it.%20I%20too%20have%20women%20in%20my%20house.%20So%2C%20we%20should%20be%20concerned%20for%20their%20safety.%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca