ia-1724916499-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Famit-lathia-1724916499-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Famit-lathia-1724916499-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-363344%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAmit%20prepares%20students%20for%20competitive%20exams%20like%20SSC%20CGL%2C%20Haryana%20Staff%20Selection%20Commission%2C%20and%20more.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20performing%20my%20duty%20as%20a%20constable%2C%20I%20would%20see%20a%20lot%20of%20children%20engaged%20in%20odd%20jobs.%20Their%20conditions%20would%20remind%20me%20of%20my%20old%20days.%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20for%20them%20so%20that%20they%20come%20out%20of%20that%20circle%20and%20secure%20a%20brighter%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20faced%20opposition%20from%20his%20family%20when%20he%20decided%20to%20devote%20himself%20entirely%20to%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20welfare%2C%20ultimately%20leading%20to%20him%20being%20kicked%20out%20of%20his%20home.%20Despite%20this%2C%20his%20determination%20remained%20unwavering%20as%20he%20continued%20to%20work%20tirelessly%20towards%20his%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CComing%20from%20an%20underprivileged%20background%2C%20I%20knew%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20the%20children.%20I%20wondered%20if%20I%20could%20secure%20a%20government%20job%2C%20then%20why%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20these%20kids%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202012%2C%20Amit%20started%20his%20first%20batch%20with%2010%20students%2C%20out%20of%20them%20six%20got%20government%20jobs.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20not%20only%20transformed%20their%20lives%20but%20also%20boosted%20my%20confidence%20as%20an%20educator.%20I%20started%20juggling%20between%20my%20job%20and%20teaching%20these%20kids.%20I%20also%20started%20devoting%20most%20of%20my%20salary%20to%20manage%20their%20expenses%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20lifelong%20commitment%20to%20serving%20others%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20Amit%20has%20mentored%20350%20students%20to%20secure%20jobs%20in%20the%20Army%2C%20police%2C%20and%20Group%20B%20and%20C%20officers%20in%20various%20departments%20of%20the%20Indian%20government.%20For%20this%2C%20he%20has%20received%20constant%20support%20from%20his%20wife%2C%20a%20few%20fellow%20officers%20and%20old%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Famit-lathia-2-1724916794.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amit%20has%20been%20recognised%20for%20his%20work%20and%20continues%20to%20be%20an%20inspiration%20for%20hundreds%20of%20underprivileged%20children.%20%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Famit-lathia-2-1724916794.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Famit-lathia-2-1724916794-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Famit-lathia-2-1724916794-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Famit-lathia-2-1724916794-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Famit-lathia-2-1724916794-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-363347%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAmit%20has%20been%20recognised%20for%20his%20work%20and%20continues%20to%20be%20an%20inspiration%20for%20hundreds%20of%20underprivileged%20children.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20wife%E2%80%99s%20unwavering%20support%20and%20dedication%20to%20the%20cause%20have%20been%20instrumental%20in%20the%20success%20of%20his%20mission.%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20my%20wedding%2C%20I%20informed%20my%20wife%20Manju%20about%20my%20purpose.%20She%20also%20stepped%20in%20and%20vowed%20to%20help%20me%20in%20the%20cause.%20Today%2C%20Manju%20is%20a%20mathematics%20professor%20in%20a%20government%20college%20in%20Sonipat.%20She%20takes%20care%20of%20all%20of%20the%20household%20expenses%20and%20often%20takes%20time%20off%20to%20teach%20the%20children.%20I%20am%20so%20grateful%20to%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20Amit%2C%20about%20five%20fellow%20officers%20and%20former%20students%20spare%20time%20to%20teach%20the%20students.%20Sonu%2C%20who%20works%20with%20the%20Delhi%20police%20and%20teaches%20English%20and%20General%20Knowledge%20to%20students%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20working%20with%20Amit%20sir%20for%20the%20past%20five%20years.%20I%20have%20witnessed%20his%20struggles.%20He%20is%20a%20selfless%20and%20dedicated%20individual.%20I%20am%20glad%20to%20be%20part%20of%20his%20cause.%20I%20also%20dedicate%202-3%20days%20in%20a%20week%20to%20teach%20students%20when%20Amit%20sir%20is%20on%20duty.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20emphasises%20the%20importance%20of%20holistic%20development%20and%20encourages%20children%20to%20explore%20various%20paths%20to%20success.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20some%20children%20secure%20government%20jobs%2C%20some%20choose%20to%20return%20to%20their%20villages%20to%20do%20farming%20after%20unsuccessful%20attempts.%20The%20aim%20is%20to%20make%20them%20self-reliant%20and%20prevent%20them%20from%20engaging%20in%20criminal%20activities%20in%20greed%20of%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20his%20perseverance%20and%20selfless%20dedication%2C%20Amit%20continues%20to%20be%20an%20inspiration%20for%20hundreds%20of%20underprivileged%20children.%20On%20his%20commitment%20to%20providing%20a%20better%20future%20for%20the%20next%20generation%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20received%20multiple%20awards%20for%20this%20work.%20But%20I%20am%20not%20doing%20this%20work%20for%20a%20%3Cem%3Epuraskar%20%3C%2Fem%3E(award)%20but%20for%20%3Cem%3Epurushartha%20%3C%2Fem%3E(purpose%20of%20human%20being).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCurrently%2C%20I%20am%20able%20to%20take%20in%20only%2030%20children%20every%20year%20due%20to%20financial%20constraints%20but%20there%20are%20so%20many%20children%20who%20require%20the%20support.%20I%20wish%20that%20more%20people%20extend%20their%20support%20for%20the%20future%20of%20these%20children.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20seek%20financial%20support%20but%20people%20can%20donate%20stationery%2C%20notebooks%2C%20old%20books%2C%20and%20dry%20ration%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photo%3A%20Amit%20Lathia.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724919280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Famit-lathia-1-1724916746.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D363341%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20police%20constable%20Amit%20Lathia%20has%20'adopted'%20more%20than%20350%20underprivileged%20children%20to%20help%20them%20secure%20government%20jobs%20by%20providing%20them%20with%20food%2C%20study%20material%20and%20a%20safe%20place%20to%20live.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Can%20a%20YouTube%20video%20really%20fix%20your%20wet%20phone%3A%20Why%20the%20answer%20is%20Yes%20and%20No%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724919095000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112890422%2Cimgsize-62124.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fcan-a-youtube-video-really-fix-your-wet-phone-why-the-answ