ndertaking%20of%20good%20work%2C%20there%20is%20bound%20to%20be%20some%20resistance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20an%20anecdote%20of%20his%20college%20days%2C%20when%20he%20was%20pursuing%20his%20MSW%20(Masters%20in%20Social%20Work)%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20very%20little%20awareness%20about%20blood%20donation%20at%20the%20time.%20I%20started%20working%20with%20a%20few%20friends%20to%20organise%20camps%20to%20encourage%20people%20to%20donate%20blood.%20But%20the%20donors%E2%80%99%20parents%20weren%E2%80%99t%20too%20happy%20about%20it.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20would%20berate%20him%20for%20forcing%20their%20wards%20into%20giving%20blood%20which%20they%20believed%20would%20%E2%80%9Cmake%20them%20less%20human%E2%80%9D.%20But%20gradually%2C%20the%20notion%20was%20dispelled%20and%20Kamble%20became%20the%20first%20point%20of%20contact%20in%20cases%20where%20someone%20needed%20blood%20for%20a%20relative%20or%20friend.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20his%20work%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F208322%2Fbengaluru-teen-teacher-death-blood-donation-community-inspiring-india-say143%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblood%20donation%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20connected%20him%20with%20doctors%2C%20paramedics%2C%20social%20workers%20and%20others%20%E2%80%94%20the%20same%20network%20that%20he%20now%20relies%20on%20for%20information%20on%20child%20marriages%20in%20Beed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20as%20Kamble%20interjects%2C%20technology%20has%20proved%20very%20resourceful%2C%20especially%20WhatsApp.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20can%20send%20the%20victims%E2%80%99%20details%20and%20pictures%20to%20the%20authorities%20and%20the%20nearest%20social%20worker.%20It%20speeds%20things%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%20Prior%20to%202015%2C%20when%20the%20app%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20as%20popular%2C%20he%20says%20it%20was%20tough%20navigating%20cases%20and%20a%20slow%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchild-marriage-5_11zon-1724158797.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Over%20the%20years%20Tatwashil%20and%20Ashok%20have%20stopped%20over%203000%20child%20marriages%20and%20helped%20hundreds%20of%20sexual%20abuse%20survivors%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchild-marriage-5_11zon-1724158797.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchild-marriage-5_11zon-1724158797-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchild-marriage-5_11zon-1724158797-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchild-marriage-5_11zon-1724158797-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchild-marriage-5_11zon-1724158797-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-362120%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EOver%20the%20years%20Tatwashil%20and%20Ashok%20have%20stopped%20over%203%2C000%20child%20marriages%20and%20helped%20hundreds%20of%20sexual%20abuse%20survivors%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Tatwashil%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20get%20tip-offs%20on%20a%20call.%20Then%20we%20would%20head%20to%20the%20authorities%20and%20collect%20documents.%20There%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20hearsay%20and%20paperwork.%20It%20was%20a%20hassle.%E2%80%9D%20He%20shares%20a%20few%20anecdotes%20of%20how%20vital%20information%20like%20the%20girl%E2%80%99s%20age%20got%20lost%20in%20conversation%20once%20or%20twice.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20reached%20the%20location%20and%20found%20out%20that%20the%20bride%20was%20well%20above%2018%20years%20old.%20We%20had%20dinner%20there%20and%20headed%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares%20in%20a%20lighter%20vein.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20in%20cases%20where%20there%20is%20an%20underage%20girl%20being%20wedded%20off%2C%20the%20duo%20maintain%20that%20halting%20a%20wedding%20is%20just%20the%20first%20step.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20then%20counsel%20the%20family%20to%20understand%20what%20led%20to%20them%20taking%20this%20step%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tangde%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20a%20police%20case%20is%20registered%20under%20The%20Prohibition%20of%20Child%20Marriage%20Act%2C%202006%20against%20the%20adults%20involved.%20If%20the%20marriage%20is%20consummated%2C%20the%20man%20is%20charged%20under%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fweb-stories%2Fwhat-is-pocso-understanding-indias-landmark-child-abuse-law%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EProtection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences%3C%2Fa%3E%20(POCSO)%20while%20the%20CWC%20takes%20the%20underage%20girl%20under%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20one%20of%20the%20most%20recent%20cases%2C%20Kamble%20says%20they%20got%20a%20tip-off%20about%20a%20child%20marriage%20that%20had%20already%20taken%20place%20a%20few%20weeks%20prior.%20%E2%80%9CI%20informed%20the%20%3Cem%3Egram%20sevika%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20asked%20her%20to%20go%20to%20the%20girl%E2%80%99s%20home.%20For%20three%20days%2C%20no%20one%20answered%20the%20door.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20fourth%20day%2C%20the%20group%20led%20by%20Kamble%20reached%20the%20house%20at%206%20am.%20They%20spoke%20to%20the%20girl%2C%20helped%20her%20re-register%20in%20the%20local%20school%2C%20and%20then%20proceeded%20to%20file%20an%20FIR%20against%20the%20family.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20girl%20is%20studying%20now%20and%20is%20happy%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kamble%20informs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsk%20the%20duo%20about%20their%20most%20challenging%20case%20and%20they%20respond%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20a%20case%2C%20but%20instead%20a%20period%20of%20time.%20%E2%80%9CChild%20marriages%20peaked%20in%20Beed%20amid%20the%20COVID-19-induced%20lockdown.%20We%20have%20more%20than%201%2C300%20villages%20here%20and%20each%20village%20witnessed%2010%20cases%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kamble%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20gatherings%20were%20less%20crowded%20and%20not%20many%20people%20in%20the%20village%20knew%20about%20these%20weddings%20because%20of%20social%20distancing%20made%20it%20tougher%20for%20the%20duo%20to%20track%20down%20the%20miscreants.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20each%20case%20they%20solve%2C%20the%20duo%20says%20it%20increases%20their%20will%20to%20do%20better.%20And%20each%20time%20they%20hear%20of%20a%20survivor%20who%20has%20risen%20to%20success%20despite%20the%20odds%2C%20it%20makes%20them%20proud.%20%E2%80%9CJust%20recently%2C%20one%20of%20the%20girl%E2%80%99s%20fathers%20came%20to%20us%20with%20%3Cem%3Epedhas%20%3C%2Fem%3E(milk%20sweets)%20to%20celebrate%20his%20daughter%20completing%20her%20BHMS%20degree%20(Bachelor%20of%20Homoeopathic%20Medicine%20and%20Surgery).%20The%20girl%20was%20rescued%20by%20us%20a%20few%20years%20ago.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20shares%20another%20story%20of%20a%20girl%20who%20recently%20scored%2093%20percent%20in%20her%20board%20exams.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20age%20of%2014%2C%20we%20had%20stopped%20her%20from%20being%20married%20off%20and%20had%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F355387%2Fmeru-international-school-tellapur-hyderabad-migrant-workers-children-daycare-learning-centre%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenrolled%20into%20school%20%3C%2Fa%3Eonce%20again.%20Her%20achievement%20is%20great.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20stories%20are%20heartening%20for%20Tangde%20and%20Kamble%2C%20they%20say%20the%20end%20goal%20is%20a%20world%20where%20girls%20do%20not%20need%20saving.%20A%20world%20where%20freedom%20will%20reign%20without%20fighting%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unicef.org%2Findia%2Fmedia%2F1176%2Ffile%2FEnding-Child-Marriage.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEnding%20Child%20Marriage%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20UNICEF%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youthpower.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FYouthPower%2Fresources%2FA%2520Statistical%2520Analysis%2520of%2520Child%2520Marriage%2520in%2520India-%2520Census%252011.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20Statistical%20Analysis%20of%20Child%20Marriage%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724398182000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchild-marriage-1724157436.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D362055%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tatwashil%20Kamble%20and%20Ashok%20Tangde%20have%20one%20goal%20--%20to%20give%20girls%20in%20Beed%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20a%20chance%20at%20a%20better%20future%20by%20saving%20them%20from%20the%20horrors%20of%20child%20marriage.%20This%20is%20the%20story%20of%20their%20mission.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F362055%2Fchild-marriages-in-beed-maharashtra-help-whistleblowers-tatwashil-kamble-ashok-tangde-whatsapp%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98You%20Don%E2%80%99t%20Need%20Delhi%20For%20UPSC%20Prep%E2%80%99%3A%20IRMS%20Officer%20On%20How%20He%20Cleared%20UPSC%20CSE%20From%20Gujarat%20Village%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%2C%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20UPSC%20coaching%20hub%20attracts%20aspirants%20from%20across%20the%20nation.%20Tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20aspirants%20continue%20to%20live%20in%20small%2C%20windowless%20PGs%20in%20popular%20and%20crowded%20areas%20of%20Mukherjee%20Nagar%2C%20Old%20Rajendra%20Nagar%20(ORN)%2C%20Patel%20Nagar%20in%20the%20hopes%20of%20becoming%20an%20officer%20one%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20believed%20that%20aspirants%20need%20to%20relocate%20to%20the%20capital%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20UPSC%20exam%20and%20that%20they%20cannot%20clear%20the%20exam%20without%20coaching.%20This%20issue%20was%20also%20highlighted%20once%20again%20when%20three%20aspirants%20recently%20lost%20their%20lives%20after%20drowning%20in%20the%20waterlogged%20basement%20of%20a%20coaching%20institute%20following%20continuous%20rainfall%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Akash%20Chavda%2C%20who%20cleared%20the%20UPSC%20examination%20in%202023%20with%20an%20All-India%20Rank%20of%201007%2C%20busts%20this%20misconception.%20He%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CDelhi%20is%20overcrowded%20with%20aspirants%20and%20this%20also%20puts%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20on%20the%20infrastructure%20there.%20When%20I%20visited%20ORN%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20I%20felt%20disgusted%20and%20suffocated.%20There%2C%20aspirants%20compromise%20on%20everything%20from%20rents%20to%20quality%20food.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20really%20do%20not%20need%20to%20go%20to%20Delhi%20for%20preparation.%20This%20could%20have%20been%20true%20a%20few%20years%20back%20when%20there%20was%20a%20lack%20of%20online%20resources%20and%20guidance.%20If%20you%20feel%20there%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20atmosphere%20for%20studies%20at%20home%2C%20you%20can%20rent%20some%20property%20in%20a%20nearby%20town%20and%20join%20a%20library.%20While%20it%20is%20not%20important%20to%20go%20to%20Delhi%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20have%20a%20mentor%20and%20a%20structured%20study%20routine%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Akash%2C%20who%20himself%20sought%20guidance%20from%20a%20retired%20DFO%20(Divisional%20Forest%20Officer)%20during%20his%20preparation%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGujarat-based%20Akash%20had%20prepared%20for%20one%20of%20the%20challenging%20examinations%20of%20the%20country%20from%20the%20comforts%20of%20his%20home%20in%20a%20small%20village%20of%20Somnath%20district.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20his%20experience%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20options%20of%20preparing%20for%20the%20exam%20by%20joining%20the%20coaching%20centres%20in%20Gandhinagar%20or%20Ahmedabad%20but%20I%20chose%20to%20remain%20in%20my%20village.%20I%20never%20felt%20left%20out.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20felt%20privileged.%20My%20mornings%20started%20with%20chirping%20birds%20and%20fresh%20air.%20Whenever%20I%20felt%20stressed%20out%2C%20I%20would%20spend%20time%20with%20my%20family.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fakash-chavda-1-1724393529.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Akash%20(second%20from%20left)%20is%20grateful%20to%20his%20cousin%20%E2%80%94%20a%20daily%20wage%20mason%20by%20profession%20%E2%80%94%20who%20showed%20him%20unwavering%20support.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fakash-chavda-1-1724393529.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fakash-chavda-1-1724393529-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fakash-chavda-1-1724393529-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fakash-chavda-1-1724393529-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fakash-chavda-1-1724393529-150x79