20immense%20contentment%20to%20Lakshmi.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20brought%20me%20closer%20to%20my%20mom%2C%20even%20though%20she%E2%80%99s%20no%20longer%20here.%20I%20sense%20that%20she%E2%80%99s%20watching%20over%20us%20as%20we%20work.%20Whenever%20I%20attend%20exhibitions%2C%20local%20people%20recognise%20me%20and%20express%20pride%20that%20I%E2%80%99ve%20kept%20the%20business%20alive%20in%20her%20memory.%20In%20some%20way%2C%20I%20believe%20we%E2%80%99re%20making%20her%20proud%2C%20and%20that%20belief%20keeps%20us%20going%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Lakshmi%20Muralidhara.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724235650000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Flakshmi-1-1724233358.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D362285%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Lakshmi's%20by%20GSB%E2%80%99%3A%20After%20losing%20her%20mother%2C%20Kerala-based%20Lakshmi%20Muralidhara%20was%20left%20with%20a%20heavy%20heart%2C%20a%20struggling%20business%2C%20and%20a%20handwritten%20recipe%20book.%20Through%20tears%20and%20laughter%2C%20she%20revamped%20the%20business%20into%20a%20multi-lakh%20venture%20that%20sells%20authentic%20homemade%20snacks%20and%20syrups.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Single%20Mom%20Starts%20%E2%80%98Papad%E2%80%99%20Biz%20With%20Women%20in%20Her%20Family%3B%20Earns%20Lakhs%20With%20Love%20for%20%E2%80%98Marwadi%20Manwar%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EI%20belong%20to%20a%20city%20renowned%20for%20its%20blue%20walls%2C%20towering%20forts%2C%20and%20history%20adorned%20with%20the%20blood%20of%20bravehearts.%20You%20guessed%20it%20right%20%E2%80%94%20overlooking%20desert%20sunsets%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20Jodhpur%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98Blue%20City%E2%80%99.%20Yet%2C%20beyond%20the%20aesthetic%20blue%20homes%20and%20royal%20heritage%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Jodhpur%20are%20celebrated%20for%20their%20tradition%20of%20%3Cem%3Emanuhar%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20%3Cem%3Emanwar%3C%2Fem%3E.%20This%20term%2C%20which%20literally%20translates%20to%20%E2%80%98coaxing%E2%80%99%2C%20culturally%20signifies%20the%20utmost%20reverence%20extended%20to%20guests%20and%20loved%20ones%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20feeding%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20we%20take%20you%20inside%20one%20such%20business%20that%20exemplifies%20this%20hospitality%20through%20its%20products.%20%E2%80%98Marwadi%20Manwar%E2%80%99%20is%20taking%20the%20authentic%20flavours%20of%20Rajasthan%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20India%20and%20beyond%20with%20their%20delicious%20homemade%20pickles%2C%20papads%2C%20and%20other%20traditional%20delicacies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20business%20is%20touching%20new%20heights%20by%20the%20day%2C%20we%20have%20a%20catch%20here.%20At%20the%20heart%20of%20Marwadi%20Manwar%20is%20Nirmala%20Shekhawat%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F237078%2Fassam-woman-entrepreneur-small-biz-pickles-homemade-homemaker-business-at-home-ang136%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20a%20woman%20who%20rose%20like%20a%20phoenix%20from%20the%20ashes%20of%20personal%20loss.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20happy%20family%2C%20comprising%20herself%2C%20her%20husband%20Karan%20Singh%20Shekhawat%2C%20and%20their%20three%20children%2C%20everything%20seemed%20to%20be%20going%20well%20for%20Nirmala%2C%20until%201%20February%2C%202020%2C%20when%20she%20lost%20her%20husband%20to%20a%20brain%20haemorrhage.%20As%20if%20this%20tragedy%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20enough%2C%20the%20COVID-19%20lockdown%20that%20followed%20brought%20financial%20struggles%2C%20adding%20to%20Nirmala%E2%80%99s%20grief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-inst