reness%20and%20oneness%20with%20nature%20is%20inoculated.%20Concepts%20are%20taught%20by%20correlating%20them%20with%20what%20they%20see%20around%20them%2C%20instead%20of%20focusing%20on%20merely%20bookish%20knowledge.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrawing%20from%20his%20own%20experiences%20as%20a%20student%20in%20Visva%20Bharathi%20university%2C%20the%20Anirvana%20school%20focuses%20on%20learning%20in%20sync%20with%20nature.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20studied%20in%20the%20open%2C%20under%20trees%20in%20Santiniketan%2C%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20nature%20and%20culture.%20Unlike%20other%20colleges%2C%20where%20the%20focus%20is%20only%20on%20textbooks%20and%20curriculum%2C%20we%20are%20taught%20to%20be%20one%20with%20nature.%20Our%20creativity%20is%20enhanced%20and%20out%20of%20the%20box%20thinking%20is%20encouraged%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Anirvana%20school%20too%2C%20children%20are%20given%20an%20opportunity%20to%20learn%20drawing%2C%20artwork%2C%20dance%2C%20music%20and%20sports.%20Professional%20artists%20visit%20the%20school%20and%20teach%20the%20children%20simple%20clay%20modelling%20and%20other%20art%20forms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20these%20children%20are%20naturally%20very%20creative%20and%20very%20good%20at%20drawing%20and%20clay%20model%20making.%20We%20want%20them%20to%20explore%20their%20talent%20with%20locally%20available%20materials%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-52-min-1724074343.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20children%20are%20taught%20art%2C%20craft%20and%20culture%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-52-min-1724074343.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media